stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Received: Client hits kgateway (Envoy)
    Received --> ExtAuthCheck: TrafficPolicy api-extauth<br/>gRPC ext_authz to OPA

    state ExtAuthCheck {
        [*] --> VerifySignature
        VerifySignature --> VerifyExpiryIssuer: RS256 ok
        VerifyExpiryIssuer --> VerifyScopes: not expired, issuer ok
        VerifyScopes --> Allowed: scope matches endpoint
        VerifySignature --> Denied: bad signature
        VerifyExpiryIssuer --> Denied: expired / wrong issuer
        VerifyScopes --> Denied: scope mismatch
    }

    Allowed --> Forwarded: Envoy forwards to sample-api
    Forwarded --> Success: backend 200
    Success --> [*]: 200 to client

    Denied --> Rejected: Envoy returns 403<br/>backend never reached
    Rejected --> [*]: 403 to client
